---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import SEO from '@/components/SEO.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEO 
    title="Shipping & Delivery Policy | AI DevOps" 
    description="Shipping and delivery policy for AI DevOps training services and digital products."
    slot="seo"
  />
  
  <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Shipping Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Digital Services Delivery</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Since AI DevOps primarily provides digital training services and online courses, most of our services are delivered electronically through our platform. The orders for digital services are processed and delivered immediately upon successful payment confirmation.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
          <h3 class="text-blue-200 font-semibold mb-2">Training Sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-200">
            Live training sessions are scheduled and delivered through our online platform. You will receive confirmation details and meeting links via email immediately after booking confirmation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Physical Products (If Applicable)</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          In case of any physical products or materials, the orders are shipped through registered domestic courier companies and/or speed post only. Orders are shipped within 1 day from the date of the order and/or payment or as per the delivery date agreed at the time of order confirmation and delivering of the shipment, subject to courier company / post office norms.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Platform Owner shall not be liable for any delay in delivery by the courier company / postal authority. Delivery of all orders will be made to the address provided by the buyer at the time of purchase.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Delivery of our services will be confirmed on your email ID as specified at the time of registration. If there are any shipping cost(s) levied by the seller or the Platform Owner (as the case be), the same is not refundable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Digital Content Delivery</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-green-900/20 border border-green-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
          <h3 class="text-green-200 font-semibold mb-2">Training Materials</h3>
          <p class="text-green-200 mb-2">Access to training materials is provided through:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-green-200 ml-4">
            <li>Online platform access immediately after payment</li>
            <li>Downloadable resources and documentation</li>
            <li>Video recordings of live sessions (where applicable)</li>
            <li>Email delivery of course materials</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Digital content is typically available immediately after successful payment processing. In case of any technical delays, our support team will ensure delivery within 24 hours of payment confirmation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Timeline</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
          <h3 class="text-yellow-200 font-semibold mb-2">Service Delivery Schedule</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-yellow-200 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Digital Access:</strong> Immediate (within 15 minutes of payment)</li>
            <li><strong>Training Session:</strong> As per scheduled time</li>
            <li><strong>Course Materials:</strong> Within 24 hours of booking</li>
            <li><strong>Certificates:</strong> Upon course completion</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Confirmation</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          You will receive delivery confirmation via email for all services. This confirmation includes:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
          <li>Service access details and login credentials</li>
          <li>Training session schedule and meeting links</li>
          <li>Download links for course materials</li>
          <li>Contact information for technical support</li>
          <li>Instructions for accessing your purchased services</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Issues</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          If you do not receive your service access details within the specified time frame, please contact our support team immediately. We will investigate and resolve the issue promptly.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
          <h3 class="text-red-200 font-semibold mb-2">Common Delivery Issues</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-red-200 ml-4">
            <li>Check your spam/junk email folder</li>
            <li>Verify the email address provided during booking</li>
            <li>Ensure payment has been processed successfully</li>
            <li>Contact support if access links are not working</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2"><strong>For delivery-related queries:</strong></p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2"><strong>Company:</strong> AI DevOps</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2"><strong>Address:</strong> A-178 Shahbad Dairy, New Delhi, India</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> Contact us through the website</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300"><strong>Phone:</strong> Available Monday - Friday (9:00 - 18:00)</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-8">
        This shipping policy is effective as of the date of your purchase and may be updated from time to time. Please check this page periodically for any changes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
